Highest Estimated AIS Score / Score AIS estimé le plus élevé

For each region, list the most severe injury / Pour chaque, lister les plus graves blessures
             

0 = uninjured / Indemne              
1 = minor  / mineur 
2 = moderate / modérée 
3 = serious  / serieuse                        
4 = severe / sévère  
5 = possibly fatal, likely to die /  peut-être fatale                   
6 = fatal (currently untreatable) / fatale (incurable)
